<title>jạʾnạ fy ạllyl ṭfl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jạʾnạ fy ạllyl ṭfl lys mn hdẖạ ạlạ̉nạm
 frạ̉ynạ ạlṭhr fyh wbh tm ạlslạm
 jạʾnạ wạllyl dạjn bynmạ ạlnạs nyạm
 wld fy byt lḥm nwrh gẖṭy̱ ạlẓlạm
 1-(qd ạ̉ty̱ ạlrʿạẗ ṣwt mn dẖry̱ ạlmjd ạlạ̉ṣyl
 ṣạr fạdy ạlkẖlq ṭflạaⁿ ạsmh ʿmạnwỷyl)2
 2-(bsẖrwạ kl ạlkẖṭạẗ yạ jmyʿ ạlʿạlmyn
 qd ạty̱ rb ạlḥyạẗ fạtbʿwh ạ̉jmʿyn)2
 3-(ạ̹ṭrḥwạ ạlḥml ʿlyh yạ jmyʿ ạlmtʿbyn
 wạsjdwạ byn ydyh wạsẖkrwh kl ḥyn)2</lyrics>
